Name: Not Without My Poop
About the game: Take control of an ambitious young dung beetle, on the journey of getting his dung ball to where it's going. Move and run around on top of a large dung ball to steer it in any direction. Controls are simple, only WASD or Arrow Keys. WARNING : This game might be frustrating, as controlling the dung ball takes significant skill and hand-eye coordination. I will not be held liable for any poop in your face.
